The understanding and comprehension of the relationship and impacts of man and technology is gained in the subject. A variety of areas of Technology will be addressed. Simple practical tasks of technology applications will be performed. As a result of teaching the student's willingness to apply the acquired knowledge creatively in technology education lessons is achieved.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the subject is to enable students to gain an overview of the technology and its various disciplines. Teaching through subject is to achieve the student's willingness to apply the acquired knowledge creatively in technology education lessons.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  1. Knows and is able to implement the technology in different areas of the classroom.  2. Is able to present and prepare systems, processes and resources of the products and equipment.  3. Is able to analyze the positive and negative effects of technology 4. Is following on ethical considerations and sustainable approach of technology.  5. Is able to write a report on important topics in the field of technology.  6. Understands the need for technological literacy. 7. Is able to creatively solve practical functions and construct technical solutions.
